HEADWORD: Recti-
<hw>Rec"ti-</hw> <pr>(r?k"t?*)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>rectus</ets>
straight.]</ety> <def>A combining form signifying <xex>straight</xex>;
<as>as, <ex>recti</ex>lineal, having straight lines;
<ex>recti</ex>nerved</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

